---
import { Video, TrendingUp, MousePointerClick, Trophy, Star } from "lucide-astro";
---

<section class="py-24 relative bg-gradient-to-br from-[#ff00c8]/10 via-transparent to-primary/5 overflow-hidden" id="afiliado">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 relative z-10">
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-[2.5rem] md:rounded-[3rem] p-6 md:p-16 border-2 md:border-4 border-[#2900ff]/30 shadow-2xl relative">
            
            <div class="absolute -top-6 md:-top-12 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FFD700] to-[#FDB931] text-black px-4 md:px-8 py-2 md:py-3 rounded-full font-black text-xs md:text-xl flex items-center gap-2 shadow-lg whitespace-nowrap z-20">
                <Star class="w-4 h-4 md:w-6 md:h-6 fill-current" />
                EXCLUSIVO PIONEROS
                <Star class="w-4 h-4 md:w-6 md:h-6 fill-current" />
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6 lg:gap-16 items-center">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-[#2900ff] dark:text-white mb-6 md:mb-8 leading-tight">
                      <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-[#2900ff]">Afiliado Estrella</span>
                        <span class="block text-xl md:text-2xl mt-2 text-primary">¡gana premios increíbles!</span>
                    </h2>
                    
                    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-8 md:mb-10">
                        Estamos premiando a los <strong class="text-primary">10 emprendedores más destacados</strong> del mes. No solo vendes, creces como referente en la industria.
                    </p>
                    
                    <div class="space-y-6">
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 group hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform">
                            <div class="w-10 h-10 md:w-12 md:h-12 rounded-full bg-[#2900ff] flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 shadow-lg">
                                <Video class="text-white w-5 h-5 md:w-6 md:h-6" />
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-base md:text-lg dark:text-white flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
                                    Creación de Contenido 
                                    <span class="hidden md:inline-block text-xs bg-[#ff00c8] text-white px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Beneficio</span>
                                </h4>
                                <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Podras se parte de nuestra estrategia de generacion de contenido para nuestras redes, donde tu marca sera protagonista.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 group hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform">
                            <div class="w-10 h-10 md:w-12 md:h-12 rounded-full bg-[#2900ff] flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 shadow-lg">
                                <TrendingUp class="text-white w-5 h-5 md:w-6 md:h-6" />
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-base md:text-lg dark:text-white flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
                                    Contenido de Alto Impacto
                                    <span class="hidden md:inline-block text-xs bg-primary text-white px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Beneficio</span>
                                </h4>
                                <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Nuestra objetivo siempre es buscar alta visibilidad para ayudar impulsar las ventas de nuestros afiliados.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 group hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform">
                            <div class="w-10 h-10 md:w-12 md:h-12 rounded-full bg-[#2900ff] flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 shadow-lg">
                                <MousePointerClick class="text-white w-5 h-5 md:w-6 md:h-6" />
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-base md:text-lg dark:text-white flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
                                    Exposición Masiva
                                    <span class="hidden md:inline-block text-xs bg-primary text-white px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Beneficio</span>
                                </h4>
                                <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Destaca en nuestras redes y campañas de publicidad nacional.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mt-8 md:mt-10 flex items-center gap-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 p-4 rounded-2xl">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-14 md:h-14 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg md:text-xl shrink-0">10</div>
                        <div>
                            <div class="font-bold text-sm md:text-base dark:text-white">Afiliados estrella</div>
                            <div class="text-xs md:text-sm text-slate-500">¡Podrías ser el próximo!</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                       <div class="w-full pt-4 text-center lg:text-left">
                        <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-xs md:text-sm italic">
                           Sujeto a disponibilidad  consultar
                            <a href="/terminos-y-condiciones" class="text-primary hover:text-[#2900ff] font-bold underline transition-colors">
                                términos y condiciones
                            </a>, 
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="relative group mt-8 lg:mt-0">
                    <div class="aspect-square bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-200 to-slate-300 dark:from-slate-800 dark:to-slate-700 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
                        <img alt="Video Recording Session" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700" src="https://inscribete.betogether.com.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/pienieros-f.jpg"/>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="hidden md:block absolute -bottom-4 -right-2 md:-bottom-6 md:-right-6 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-4 md:p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700 animate-float z-10 max-w-[200px] md:max-w-none">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 md:gap-4">
                            <div class="w-10 h-10 md:w-12 md:h-12 bg-[#2900ff] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white shrink-0">
                                <Trophy class="w-5 h-5 md:w-6 md:h-6" />
                            </div>
                            <div >
                                <div class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase text-slate-400">Haz Parte</div>
                                <div class="text-base md:text-lg font-black dark:text-white">del Equipo</div>
                                <div class="text-[10px] md:text-sm text-primary font-bold">#1 en ventas</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>